article.description: — Orlando Robinson had 22 points as Fresno State got past Cal State Northridge 61-43 on Saturday.
article.headline: Robinson carries Fresno St. past CS Northridge 61-43
article.linkText: Robinson carries Fresno St. past CS Northridge 61-43
article.story: FRESNO, Calif. -- — Orlando Robinson had 22 points as Fresno State got past Cal State Northridge 61-43 on Saturday. Deon Stroud had 14 points for Fresno State (7-1), which earned its fifth consecutive home victory. Jordan Campbell added 11 points. Isaiah Hill had 10 points. Elijah Hardy had 12 points for the Matadors (3-4). Onyi Eyisi added 11 points. Darius Beane had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
